Title: [ANN][ICO] APIS - The First Masternode Mediation Platform(Pre-sale in Feb.20th)

The ICO(crowdsale) will take contributions in Ethereum and Qtum, and will be conducted with smart contract on both ends.  How to participate:  1) ETH and Qtum smart contract addresses will be revealed on the crowdsale starting time on 17:00 (UTC+8) Mar 4 2018 through our official website http://apisplatform.io 2) Send your ETH or Qtum to the revealed smart contract address 3) Claim your tokens. In order to claim your tokens from our website, you must go through our KYC process.  *All relevant important information including news about listing our token on exchanges or KYC registration announcement will be sent to the email you registered on our website, so please be sure to register on our official website first!

Yes, the presale was conducted in QTUM only and ICO will be conducted QTUM and Ethereum. Author: APIS_Tom
Title: [ANN][ICO] APIS - The First Masternode Mediation Platform(Pre-sale in Feb.20th)
Body: Please see below for the official message regarding the presale from our CEO:  Dear APIS supporters, I am Ronny Yoo, CEO of APIS.  I would like to explain about the early termination of pre-sale which most of you are curious about. While we were preparing for the pre-sale, we spent a lot of time coming up with methods to provide all our investors with equal investment opportunities. Among some of the roadblocks that we confronted while seeking the optimal solution was  Qtum’s long block generation time.  This issue troubled us the most as we judged that if too many participants were to be concentrated in a single block, Qtum’s long blocktime may change participation priority depending on the gas price.  In order to prevent this unnecessary competition, we set a fixed value for the gas price and made everyone participate in the pre-sale under the same condition. However, when the pre-sale actually started, we recognized that there were a number of transactions that were not processed properly.  Our development team was monitoring all of the transactions real-time and found out that most of the transactions that failed had their gas price set at 69, not 70. The real problem occurred when we found out that the percentage of people who invested with gas price of 69 was excessively high(53% of the total transactions, to be exact). At this point, we came to the conclusion that the gas price could have been modified due to network or wallet error, and that ongoing smart contract needed to be stopped immediately for investor protection. Therefore, we stopped the original smart contract and came up with a new smart contract address urgently that had no gas price limit and were finally able to resume the pre-sale. But as the pre-sale went on with the new smart contract address, the morality of creating a new smart contract address was questioned  within our team. We subsequently came to a conclusion that the second smart contract could go against our original principle of fairness and that the contract must be closed. This is why we terminated our pre-sale earlier than scheduled.  We are still running internal tests to understand the exact cause of sudden gas price change. All relevant information regarding this incident had already been passed to the Qtum foundation, and we are looking into the issue together  I would like to express my sincere gratitude to those that participated in our pre-sale and also apologize to those who were unable to do so. We will keep you updated on this issue.  I will talk briefly about our future operation plan. Adhering to our core principle of enlarging the blockchain industry and protecting investors’ assets, we will never resell our remaining tokens from the pre-sale. All unsold tokens(254,584,967 tokens) will be promptly burnt after the termination of ICO with a prior announcement.  Thank you.  Best regards, Ronny Yoo

Author: APIS_Tom
Title: [ANN][ICO] APIS - The First Masternode Mediation Platform(Pre-sale in Feb.20th)
Body: This is how it would work in principle:  You can decide to invest in whichever coin's masternode that you desire.  You would go to the APIS platform, buy APIS coins which gives you access to masternode investment system in the platform.  Once you choose the type of coin and how much APIS you want to put towards it, you can set up a masternode.  After the masternode is active, you can get rewards based on that coin's ROI. The reward can be withdrawn through APIS or other coins, so in addition to the APIS masternode it allows some hedging against potential up/downs.  While this may not be so different from setting up your masternode, APIS has some major benefits:  1. The entire operation is relatively decentralized- there is no need to "give" your coin to some stranger's hands  2. No need to set up servers and satisfy network requirements as APIS will do this for you  3. You have a range of masternode coins that you can invest on freely  4. You do not have to have a huge principle investment(i.e. 1000DASH) to form a masternode, but your ROI will be the same.  5. You can withdraw your coins anytime you want- which is not true for masternode brokers existent on the market today.

Author: APIS_Tom
Title: [ANN][ICO] APIS - The First Masternode Mediation Platform(Pre-sale in Feb.20th)
Body: Announcement to all readers:  We are proud to announce the first meetup for our APIS project, which aimes to be the first cryptocurrency platform to provide investment services for masternodes.    The meetup will be held in Seoul, Korea on 8 Feb 2018, 7:00PM local time with our meetup partners fidentiaX and Beluga Pay. The location is called JBK convention hall, located in Gangnam district, Seoul City.    The purpose of this meetup will be to introduce APIS platform, fidentiaX and Beluga Pay to crytocurrency investor community of Korea, which is deemed to be one of the most passionate market for cryptocurrency and blockchain technology.  We are planning to answer detailed investor questions specifically pertaining to APIS platform, so you are most welcome to join us should you be interested in participating in our token sales event.  You can register to participate in our meetup through the on-off mix website provided below:  https://onoffmix.com/event/127170  While we have a limit to the number of participants that could actually come to our meetup, a live video link will be provided to allow those who cannot come to watch our meetup online.  We would also like to let our registered users know that the KYC process for APIS Platform Pre-sale and ICO is currently ongoing and will last until 12:00 UTC 10 Feb 2018.  It is essential for our potential investors to submit their KYC information through our website in order to participate in our Pre-sale or the ICO.  Please follow the guide provided at our official website https://apisplatform.io/ to submit your KYC application if you wish to participate in either of our token sales event.  The KYC registration process will end on 12:00 UTC 10 Feb 2018 and participants will be notified of their successful registration shortly after.  Thank you again for your interest in APIS platform and we hope to see you all at the meetup.

Author: APIS_Tom
Title: [ANN][ICO] APIS - The First Masternode Mediation Platform(Pre-sale in Feb.20th)
Body: I am not sure if I understand your question correctly but I will try to answer what I think your question is.  APIS is a investment tool/platform through which you can invest in masternodes of other coins.  In order to use the APIS platform, you will need to buy APIS tokens (from exchanges or at the platform, up to you).  After you buy APIS tokens you will be shown different masternode pools that you can join.  If you choose join and form a complete masternode, you will get principle+reward after the masternode reward time has passed for that specific coin that you invested in.  Therefore, your APIS tokens will be locked for however long it takes for your masternode to give you a reward.  If you choose to withdraw before the reward time(block), you will still get your principle investment but not the reward.  Hope this answers your question.

Author: APIS_Tom
Title: [ANN][ICO] APIS - The First Masternode Mediation Platform(Pre-sale in Feb.20th)
Body: For clarification, this only applies to the APIS token masternodes. There will be NO bonus for investors investing large amounts of APIS tokens into other masternode coins. Author: RedCliffdoll
Title: [ANN][ICO] APIS - The First Masternode Mediation Platform(Pre-sale in Feb.20th)
Body: Homepage        ANN Telegram        Official Telegram        APIS Whitepaper <- Link of WhitePaper    APIS(Advanced Property Investment System)    Introduction and Problem Statement  The APIS is building a “Masternode Mediation Platform” to familiarize the term “masternode” to a larger range of people and to let them enjoy the advantages and benefits of a masternode. A masternode’s most distinctive feature is that any investor investing in a masternode can acquire stable and almost guaranteed profit just by locking up his/her money in the masternode for a fixed amount of time. However, despite its attractive characteristic, hosting a masternode is quite out of reach for most normal people since most masternodes require substantial amount of capital and intricate software engineering to set one up. By aiding these normal individuals come together to form a whole masternode, we will be able to encourage more people to participate in masternode investments as well as to provide them with much safer way of investing money rather than investing in the exchange market without adequate knowledge.   Token Sale     Our APIS Token Sale amount this time is 5,236,000,000 APIS which is 55% of the total APIS and it is worth 1,000,000 QTUM. Our sale this time will be divided into 3 main stages :   Private Offering Stage   Coins Allocated : 1,380,000,000 APIS / 240,000 QTUM  Many leaders of related field, companies and angel investors contributed to the establishment and development of the APIS platform. As a return for that, we are giving bonus of 15%. In other words,  1QTUM = 5,750APIS  The Total Cap for this stage is 240 ,000 QTUM.   Pre-sale Stage   Coins Allocated : 756,000,000 APIS / 140,000 QTUM As a means of appreciation for APIS early investors, we are planning to sell APIS through Qtum Smart Contract before the actual crowd sale begins. There will be 8% of bonus given.  1QTUM = 5,400 APIS  The Total Cap for this stage is 140,000 QTUM   Crowd Sale Stage   Coins Allocated : 3,100,000,000 APIS / 620,000 QTUM In the Crowd Sale stage, we are planning to sell APIS through Qtum Smart Contract.    1QTUM=5,000APIS  The Total Cap for this stage is 620,000 QTUM  In this stage, we will set-up global communities and get investments from the general public for the development of the APIS Platform.  Participation Routes : Official Website, Platforms in countries like Singapore, England, Russia, Japan, Canada and Thailand. Currency Supported : QTUM      For details, please refer to our “APIS Whitepaper Ver.5.5.1”  Feedbacks welcome.    Homepage        ANN Telegram        Official Telegram        APIS Whitepaper <- Link of WhitePaper
